      "content": "okay but if the data shows that the government systems actually work better for public health and stop people from going broke, isnt it kind of weird to keep calling it just an \"opinion\"? like if the results are objectively better for society, doesn't that make the \"right to healthcare\" more of a reality than just a theory?",
